comment.author: 26881258@N07
comment._content: The registration can just be read on the side of the fuselage Go.G.IV 22/17 (Ssw) It is a Gotha G.IV which was built in license by the Siemens Schuckert Werke (S.S.W.). This machine is one from a series of 40 machines license built by S.S.W. with serials 200/17 till 239/17.
